Aberdeen Asset Management plc is an international investment management group , managingassets for both institutions and private individuals from offices around the world . It is based in Aberdeen in Scotland and listed on the London Stock Exchange ( LSE : ADN ) . The company is a constituent of the FTSE 250 Index . The company was established in 1876 . It operates mainly in the United Kingdom but has a growing presences worldwide , particularly Asia , Oceania and the Americas . As of December 2006 it had funds under management of Â£75.6 billion . 